# Loewenstark_Alternativeproduct
Creates alternative product carousel from alternative sku field with comma separated list.
This module comes with several settings that have to be made.

###Attribute install
<ul>
<li>Add new product attribute with attribute code: alternative_products</li>
<li>is_html_allowed_on_front: yes</li>
<li>is_visible_on_front: yes</li>
<li>used_in_product_listing: yes</li>
<li>Add this attribute to general product attribute-set</li>
</ul>

List created by comma-separeted sku list from this alternative_products field im Backend
Refresh cache, reindex.

